]]></screen>
    </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    例子：
<screen><![CDATA[
SELECT xpath_exists('/my:a/text()', '<my:a xmlns:my="http://example.com">test</my:a>',
                     ARRAY[ARRAY['my', 'http://example.com']]);

